{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-component-tsx","path":"/component/Message/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"3073c598-31ce-5381-bd2b-6e3f0881d224","excerpt":"简介 对用户的操作作出轻量的全局反馈。全局展示操作反馈信息。 可提供成功、警告和错误等反馈信息。 顶部居中显示并自动消失，是一种不打断用户操作的轻量级提示方式。 基本构成  图标（A） 标题（B） 信息（C） 操作按钮（D） 关闭按钮（D） √ √ √ √ √ A.图标（必选） 告知用户通知的类型 B…","html":"<!--副标题具体写法见源代码模式-->\n<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<p>对用户的操作作出轻量的全局反馈。全局展示操作反馈信息。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>可提供成功、警告和错误等反馈信息。</li>\n<li>顶部居中显示并自动消失，是一种不打断用户操作的轻量级提示方式。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"基本构成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"基本构成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本构成</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Basic\"\n        title=\"Basic\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/3530fcb153e7ab42b6fb1f1e6605d348/37523/Basic.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/3530fcb153e7ab42b6fb1f1e6605d348/f21e7/Basic.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/3530fcb153e7ab42b6fb1f1e6605d348/37523/Basic.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">图标（A）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">标题（B）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">信息（C）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">操作按钮（D）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">关闭按钮（D）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>A.图标（必选）</strong></p>\n<p>告知用户通知的类型</p>\n<p><strong>B.标题（必选）</strong></p>\n<p>为用户提供通知的快速概述</p>\n<p><strong>C.信息（必选）</strong></p>\n<p>提供通知更详细的信息</p>\n<p><strong>D.操作按钮（必选）</strong></p>\n<p>为用户提供通知相关的查看或处理入口</p>\n<p><strong>D.关闭按钮（必选）</strong></p>\n<p>关闭通知</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本状态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"基本状态 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本状态</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 776px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 110.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"States\"\n        title=\"States\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/47bdda29933610990fa2bdc233281ec5/167b5/States.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/47bdda29933610990fa2bdc233281ec5/f21e7/States.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/47bdda29933610990fa2bdc233281ec5/37523/States.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/47bdda29933610990fa2bdc233281ec5/167b5/States.png 776w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 776px) 100vw, 776px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n### 正常的文本</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 698px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/623322c9a46be9b721c17b694fef3d6f/487bb/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/623322c9a46be9b721c17b694fef3d6f/f21e7/4.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/623322c9a46be9b721c17b694fef3d6f/487bb/4.png 698w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 698px) 100vw, 698px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n3行内文本，高度自适应</p>\n<h3 id=\"超长的文本（不建议）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B6%85%E9%95%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"超长的文本（不建议） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>超长的文本（不建议）</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/b15a8015d1fbf00a72ef2192e0b7dbb4/a6d36/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/b15a8015d1fbf00a72ef2192e0b7dbb4/f21e7/5.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/b15a8015d1fbf00a72ef2192e0b7dbb4/a6d36/5.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n文本超过3行，出滚动条，滚动展示</p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<!--可以做一个gif-->\n<p>气泡确认框没有蒙层，点击确认框以外的区域即可关闭。</p>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"避免滥用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"避免滥用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>避免滥用</h3>\n<p>气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> 是会打断用户操作流的设计，是迫不得已的折中方案：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>其会增加用户操作步骤，降低操作效率；</li>\n<li>打断用户流程，降低转化率；</li>\n<li>影响产品品质，损害用户体验印象。\n所以要不要选择使用 气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> ，需要从多个因素去权衡利弊。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>低成本的操作</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>对于低成本的操作可以不设置二次确认。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>举个例子：从操作频率上讲：录入表单，或者新建一个表单，查看详情都是最最最最基本操作，所以无需设置二次确认。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>中成本的操作</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>操作之后，会使其产生较严重的后果，但并不至于造成不可挽回的后果。所以我们可以在产生严重后果之前设置 气泡确认框 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code> ，确认操作，并提醒即将产生的结果。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>高成本操作</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在操作后会产生很严重或者不可挽回的后果，需要让用户仔细想清楚的时候，提前预知操作风险，阻断流程并且再次确认。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>比如删除账号、修改数据、提交/发送重要内容时，可以使用弹窗 <code class=\"language-text\">PopConfirm</code>直接打断用户。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"u-md-flex-without-bg\">\n   <div class=\"u-md-mr24\">\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-suggested\"></i>对于中成本的操作，提示用户可能会带来的后果，以及用户可以执行什么操作。</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 698px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.388888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/314a60aa3878b9fc80d3e17a9ffced99/487bb/6.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/314a60aa3878b9fc80d3e17a9ffced99/f21e7/6.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/314a60aa3878b9fc80d3e17a9ffced99/487bb/6.png 698w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 698px) 100vw, 698px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-not-suggested\"></i>对低成本的操作进行确认，会显得多此一举。</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 784px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 51.388888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/0e99560072797fba8ce16339b7655d3f/4971b/2.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/0e99560072797fba8ce16339b7655d3f/f21e7/2.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/0e99560072797fba8ce16339b7655d3f/37523/2.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/0e99560072797fba8ce16339b7655d3f/4971b/2.png 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 784px) 100vw, 784px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"相关文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相关文档</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Popover/\">Popover 气泡卡片</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Tooltip/\">Tooltip 文字提示</a></li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"value":"简介","depth":2},{"value":"基本构成","depth":2},{"value":"基本状态","depth":2},{"value":"超长的文本（不建议）","depth":3},{"value":"设计说明","depth":2},{"value":"常见问题","depth":2},{"value":"避免滥用","depth":3},{"value":"相关文档","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Message/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":"用于中成本的操作的二次确认。","order":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3073c598-31ce-5381-bd2b-6e3f0881d224","previousPostId":"59e0695a-37c4-56d7-83d6-1556f60cba52","nextPostId":"359e9ef0-aea6-5e0d-a3f6-b3413558b402"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3000541721","850322689"]}